And how much the series has degraded since the third season! But there were nasty communists! oh, i'm sorry, bloody, stupid, cruel, nasty communists!
Do you really like to watch absolutely ridiculous, delusional myths being cultivated? And they do this shit INSTEAD of this beautiful series.
